---
title: Lemon Pepper Halloumi Tacos with Greek-Style Yoghurt & Cucumber Salad
description: Taco night gets a zesty twist with a helping hand from sweet and savoury lemon pepper halloumi! Pair with a crunchy cucumber salad, then wrap up in soft tortillas and top with a dollop of tangy Greek-style yoghurt. Bright, bold and bursting with flavour these tacos are a fiesta you won’t want to miss!
